data.description: Come View and Purchase This Home, Unique Floor Plan with an Open Concept, Beautifully Designed with such Custom and attention paid  to Detail, Formal Dining Room across from Formal Living Room. Two View Natural Gas Fireplace between the Formal Living Room and Dining Room, with Quality Custom Framing with Mantle with, Wainscoating, Gourmet Kitchen with Cooktop and Wall Oven, Custom Quality Cabinets,  Over Looks Family Room Large Primary Bedroom on the Other side of the Home, Primary Bath with Two Person Ceramic Shower with Seat, Jack and Jill Bedrooms on the Other side of the Home with Their Own Full Bathroom,  Take a Serious Look at the Finished Room Over The garage That's over 872 SQFT, This is the Size of the Finished Room Over This Three Car Garage, Endless Possibilities for this Game Room, Storage Galore, There is nothing simple about this Home, Such attention has been paid to Detail, The Deck overlooks the Gigantic backyard with a View of the Lake, Come View and Purchase!
